{
  "video_id": "gpE_W50OTUc",
  "title": "How to find the person who can help you get ahead at work | Carla Harris",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12520.0,
      "end_time": 16576.0,
      "text": "It was the spring of 1988"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16600.0,
      "end_time": 19776.0,
      "text": "when I had the aha moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19800.0,
      "end_time": 22336.0,
      "text": "I was at my first roundtable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22360.0,
      "end_time": 24216.0,
      "text": "and for those of you who don&#39;t know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24240.0,
      "end_time": 28174.0,
      "text": "the roundtable was a very commonly used phrase on Wall Street"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28200.0,
      "end_time": 31416.0,
      "text": "to describe the year-end evaluative process"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31440.0,
      "end_time": 35896.0,
      "text": "for analysts, associates, vice presidents, all the way up to managing directors."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35920.0,
      "end_time": 40176.0,
      "text": "That was the process where they were discussed behind closed doors"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40200.0,
      "end_time": 43176.0,
      "text": "around a table, i.e. the round table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43200.0,
      "end_time": 45696.0,
      "text": "and everyone was put into a category --"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45720.0,
      "end_time": 49376.0,
      "text": "the top bucket, the middle bucket, the lower bucket --"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49400.0,
      "end_time": 52336.0,
      "text": "and then that was translated into a bonus range"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52360.0,
      "end_time": 55256.0,
      "text": "that would be assigned to each professional."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55280.0,
      "end_time": 58696.0,
      "text": "This was my first time there, and as I observed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58720.0,
      "end_time": 62160.0,
      "text": "I saw that there was one person that was responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62400.0,
      "end_time": 65295.0,
      "text": "for recording the outcome of a conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65319.0,
      "end_time": 68295.0,
      "text": "There were other people in the room that had the responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68320.0,
      "end_time": 70535.0,
      "text": "of presenting the cases of all the candidates."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70560.0,
      "end_time": 74696.0,
      "text": "And there were other invited guests who were supposed to comment"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 74720.0,
      "end_time": 77720.0,
      "text": "as a candidate&#39;s position was presented."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78440.0,
      "end_time": 82960.0,
      "text": "It was interesting to me that those other people"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82120.0,
      "end_time": 85856.0,
      "text": "were folks who were more senior than the folks that were being discussed"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85880.0,
      "end_time": 90216.0,
      "text": "and they theoretically had had some interaction with those candidates."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 90240.0,
      "end_time": 94560.0,
      "text": "Now, I was really excited to be at this roundtable for the first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 94800.0,
      "end_time": 97655.0,
      "text": "because I knew that my own process would go through this same way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 97680.0,
      "end_time": 100736.0,
      "text": "and that my bonus would be decided in the same way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100760.0,
      "end_time": 102576.0,
      "text": "so I wanted to know how it worked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102600.0,
      "end_time": 104136.0,
      "text": "but more importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 104160.0,
      "end_time": 107776.0,
      "text": "I wanted to understand how this concept of a meritocracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 107800.0,
      "end_time": 111216.0,
      "text": "that every company that I talked to walking out of business school"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 111240.0,
      "end_time": 112455.0,
      "text": "was selling."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 112480.0,
      "end_time": 114960.0,
      "text": "Every time I talked to a company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 114120.0,
      "end_time": 118296.0,
      "text": "they would say, \"Our culture, our process, is a meritocracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 118320.0,
      "end_time": 121336.0,
      "text": "The way you get ahead in this organization is that you&#39;re smart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 121360.0,
      "end_time": 123616.0,
      "text": "you put your head down and you work really hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123640.0,
      "end_time": 125256.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;ll go right to the top."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 125280.0,
      "end_time": 128616.0,
      "text": "So here was my opportunity to see exactly how that worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128639.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130775.00000000001,
      "text": "So as the process began,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 130800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 134960.0,
      "text": "I heard the recorder call the first person&#39;s name."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134120.0,
      "end_time": 135816.0,
      "text": "\"Joe Smith.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135840.0,
      "end_time": 140136.0,
      "text": "The person responsible for presenting Joe&#39;s case did just that."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 140160.0,
      "end_time": 143176.0,
      "text": "Three quarters of the way through, someone interrupted and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143200.0,
      "end_time": 145456.0,
      "text": "\"This is a great candidate, outstanding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145480.0,
      "end_time": 148296.0,
      "text": "has great analytical and quantitative skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 148320.0,
      "end_time": 150136.0,
      "text": "This is a superstar.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 150160.0,
      "end_time": 151656.0,
      "text": "The recorder then said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 151680.0,
      "end_time": 154760.0,
      "text": "\"Sounds like Joe should go in the top bucket.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 155440.0,
      "end_time": 157536.0,
      "text": "Second person, Mary Smith."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 157560.0,
      "end_time": 161376.0,
      "text": "Halfway through that presentation, someone said, \"Solid candidate."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 161400.0,
      "end_time": 164416.0,
      "text": "Nothing really special, but a good pair of hands.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164440.0,
      "end_time": 165776.0,
      "text": "The recorder said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 165800.0,
      "end_time": 168416.0,
      "text": "\"Sounds like Mary should go in the middle bucket.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 168440.0,
      "end_time": 171176.0,
      "text": "And then someone said, \"Arnold Smith.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 171200.0,
      "end_time": 174456.0,
      "text": "Before the person could present Arnold&#39;s case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 174480.0,
      "end_time": 178296.0,
      "text": "somebody said, \"Disaster. Disaster. This kid doesn&#39;t have a clue."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 178320.0,
      "end_time": 179656.0,
      "text": "Can&#39;t do a model.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 179680.0,
      "end_time": 182176.0,
      "text": "And before the case was presented,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 182200.0,
      "end_time": 183495.0,
      "text": "the recorder said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 183520.0,
      "end_time": 186736.0,
      "text": "\"Sounds like Arnold should go in the bottom bucket.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 186760.0,
      "end_time": 190176.0,
      "text": "It was at that moment that I clutched my pearls --"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 190200.0,
      "end_time": 193495.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 193520.0,
      "end_time": 197000.0,
      "text": "and said, \"Who is going to speak for me?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 198320.0,
      "end_time": 200495.0,
      "text": "Who is going to speak for me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 200520.0,
      "end_time": 204896.0,
      "text": "It was that moment that I realized that this idea of a meritocracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 204920.0,
      "end_time": 209456.0,
      "text": "that every organizations sells is really just a myth."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 209480.0,
      "end_time": 214536.0,
      "text": "You cannot have a 100 percent meritocratic environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 214560.0,
      "end_time": 218936.0,
      "text": "when there is a human element involved in the evaluative equation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 218960.0,
      "end_time": 220816.0,
      "text": "because by definition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 220840.0,
      "end_time": 223336.0,
      "text": "that makes it subjective."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 223360.0,
      "end_time": 228816.0,
      "text": "I knew at that moment that somebody would have to be behind closed doors"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 228840.0,
      "end_time": 231536.0,
      "text": "arguing on my behalf,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 231560.0,
      "end_time": 234536.0,
      "text": "presenting content in such a way"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 234560.0,
      "end_time": 237936.0,
      "text": "that other decision makers around that table"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 237960.0,
      "end_time": 240240.0,
      "text": "would answer in my best favor."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 241400.0,
      "end_time": 243935.0,
      "text": "That was a really interesting lesson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 243960.0,
      "end_time": 247136.0,
      "text": "and then I said to myself, \"Well, who is that person?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 247160.0,
      "end_time": 249160.0,
      "text": "What do you call this person?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 249400.0,
      "end_time": 252775.0,
      "text": "And as I thought about the popular business terms at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 252800.0,
      "end_time": 256256.0,
      "text": "I said, wow, this person can&#39;t be a mentor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 256279.0,
      "end_time": 260895.0,
      "text": "because a mentor&#39;s job is to give you tailored advice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 260920.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264736.0,
      "text": "tailored specifically to you and to your career aspirations."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 264760.0,
      "end_time": 268550.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re the ones who give you the good, the bad and the ugly"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 268790.0,
      "end_time": 269839.0,
      "text": "in a no-holds-barred way."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 270839.0,
      "end_time": 275160.0,
      "text": "OK. Person can&#39;t be a champion or an advocate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 275400.0,
      "end_time": 278616.0,
      "text": "because you don&#39;t necessarily have to spend any currency"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 278640.0,
      "end_time": 280296.0,
      "text": "to be someone&#39;s champion."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 280320.0,
      "end_time": 282896.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t necessarily get invited to the room"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 282920.0,
      "end_time": 285976.0,
      "text": "behind closed doors if you&#39;re an advocate."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 286000.0,
      "end_time": 288960.0,
      "text": "It was almost two years later"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 288120.0,
      "end_time": 291816.0,
      "text": "when I realized what this person should be called."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 291840.0,
      "end_time": 294335.0,
      "text": "I was speaking at the University of Michigan"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 294360.0,
      "end_time": 296256.0,
      "text": "to the MBA candidates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 296280.0,
      "end_time": 298376.0,
      "text": "talking about the lessons that I had learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 298400.0,
      "end_time": 300455.0,
      "text": "after my three short years on Wall Street,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 300480.0,
      "end_time": 302560.0,
      "text": "and then it came to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 302800.0,
      "end_time": 305816.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Oh, this person that is carrying your interest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 305840.0,
      "end_time": 309150.0,
      "text": "or as I like to say, carrying your paper into the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 309400.0,
      "end_time": 310576.0,
      "text": "this person who is spending"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 310600.0,
      "end_time": 313976.0,
      "text": "their valuable political and social capital on you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 314000.0,
      "end_time": 318560.0,
      "text": "this person who is going to pound the table on your behalf,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 318800.0,
      "end_time": 320560.0,
      "text": "this is a sponsor."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 321600.0,
      "end_time": 324400.0,
      "text": "This is a sponsor.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 324800.0,
      "end_time": 326936.0,
      "text": "And then I said to myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 326960.0,
      "end_time": 329496.0,
      "text": "\"Well, how do you get a sponsor?"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 329520.0,
      "end_time": 332135.0,
      "text": "And frankly, why do you need one?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 332160.0,
      "end_time": 333936.0,
      "text": "Well, you need a sponsor, frankly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 333960.0,
      "end_time": 335335.0,
      "text": "because as you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 335360.0,
      "end_time": 338656.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s not one evaluative process that I can think of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 338680.0,
      "end_time": 342296.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s in academia, health care, financial services,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 342320.0,
      "end_time": 345640.0,
      "text": "not one that does not have a human element."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 346120.0,
      "end_time": 349960.0,
      "text": "So that means it has that measure of subjectivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 349120.0,
      "end_time": 354696.0,
      "text": "There is a measure of subjectivity in who is presenting your case."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 354720.0,
      "end_time": 356776.0,
      "text": "There is a measure of subjectivity"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 356800.0,
      "end_time": 358856.0,
      "text": "in what they say"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 358880.0,
      "end_time": 362656.0,
      "text": "and how they interpret any objective data that you might have."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 362680.0,
      "end_time": 368376.0,
      "text": "There is a measure of subjectivity in how they say what they&#39;re going to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 368400.0,
      "end_time": 370655.0,
      "text": "to influence the outcome."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 370680.0,
      "end_time": 374936.0,
      "text": "So therefore, you need to make sure that that person who is speaking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 374960.0,
      "end_time": 376416.0,
      "text": "that sponsor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 376440.0,
      "end_time": 378695.0,
      "text": "has your best interests at heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 378720.0,
      "end_time": 382776.0,
      "text": "and has the power to get it, whatever it is for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 382800.0,
      "end_time": 385216.0,
      "text": "to get it done behind closed doors."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 385240.0,
      "end_time": 387896.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m asked all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 387920.0,
      "end_time": 389976.0,
      "text": "\"How do you get one?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 390000.0,
      "end_time": 396136.0,
      "text": "Well, frankly, nirvana is when someone sees you in an environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 396160.0,
      "end_time": 399216.0,
      "text": "and decides, \"I&#39;m going to make it happen for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 399240.0,
      "end_time": 402160.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to make sure that you are successful.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 402400.0,
      "end_time": 405856.0,
      "text": "But for many of us in this room, we know it doesn&#39;t really happen that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 405880.0,
      "end_time": 409256.0,
      "text": "So let me introduce this concept of currency"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 409280.0,
      "end_time": 414256.0,
      "text": "and talk to you about how it impacts your ability to get a sponsor."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 414280.0,
      "end_time": 418736.0,
      "text": "There are two types of currency in any environment:"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 418760.0,
      "end_time": 422416.0,
      "text": "performance currency and relationship currency."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 422440.0,
      "end_time": 426560.0,
      "text": "And performance currency is the currency that is generated"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 426800.0,
      "end_time": 429736.0,
      "text": "by your delivering that which was asked of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 429760.0,
      "end_time": 431695.0,
      "text": "and a little bit extra."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 431720.0,
      "end_time": 436376.0,
      "text": "Every time you deliver upon an assignment above people&#39;s expectations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 436400.0,
      "end_time": 438496.0,
      "text": "you generate performance currency."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 438520.0,
      "end_time": 441376.0,
      "text": "It works exactly like the stock market."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 441400.0,
      "end_time": 443575.0,
      "text": "Any time a company says to the street"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 443600.0,
      "end_time": 445776.0,
      "text": "that they will deliver 25 cents a share"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 445800.0,
      "end_time": 448560.0,
      "text": "and that company delivers 40 cents a share,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 448800.0,
      "end_time": 450520.0,
      "text": "that stock goes up, and so will yours."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 451800.0,
      "end_time": 454560.0,
      "text": "Performance currency is valuable for three reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 454800.0,
      "end_time": 457455.0,
      "text": "Number one, it will get you noticed."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 457480.0,
      "end_time": 459936.0,
      "text": "It will create a reputation for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 459960.0,
      "end_time": 464960.0,
      "text": "Number two, it will also get you paid and promoted"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 464120.0,
      "end_time": 466536.0,
      "text": "very early on in your career"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 466560.0,
      "end_time": 469576.0,
      "text": "and very early on in any environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 469600.0,
      "end_time": 472576.0,
      "text": "And number three, it may attract a sponsor."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 472600.0,
      "end_time": 475576.0,
      "text": "Why? Because strong performance currency"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 475600.0,
      "end_time": 479696.0,
      "text": "raises your level of visibility in the environment, as I said earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 479720.0,
      "end_time": 483216.0,
      "text": "such that a sponsor may be attracted to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 483240.0,
      "end_time": 486600.0,
      "text": "Why? Because everybody loves a star."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 487360.0,
      "end_time": 491456.0,
      "text": "But if you find yourself in a situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 491480.0,
      "end_time": 493696.0,
      "text": "where you don&#39;t have a sponsor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 493720.0,
      "end_time": 495216.0,
      "text": "here&#39;s the good news."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 495240.0,
      "end_time": 499120.0,
      "text": "Remember that you can exercise your power and ask for one."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 500280.0,
      "end_time": 505296.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s where the other currency is now most important."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 505320.0,
      "end_time": 507976.0,
      "text": "That is the relationship currency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 508000.0,
      "end_time": 511736.0,
      "text": "and relationship currency is the currency that is generated"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 511760.0,
      "end_time": 516936.0,
      "text": "by the investments that you make in the people in your environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 516960.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521456.00000000006,
      "text": "the investments that you make in the people in your environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 521480.0,
      "end_time": 525416.0,
      "text": "You cannot ask someone to use their hard-earned"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 525440.0,
      "end_time": 528496.0,
      "text": "personal influential currency on your behalf"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 528520.0,
      "end_time": 531216.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;ve never had any interaction with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 531240.0,
      "end_time": 533390.0,
      "text": "It is not going to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 533559.0,
      "end_time": 539160.0,
      "text": "So it is important that you invest the time to connect, to engage"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 539400.0,
      "end_time": 542960.0,
      "text": "and to get to know the people that are in your environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 542120.0,
      "end_time": 546776.0,
      "text": "and more importantly to give them the opportunity to know you."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 546800.0,
      "end_time": 548815.0,
      "text": "Because once they know you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 548840.0,
      "end_time": 552256.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a higher probability that when you approach them"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 552280.0,
      "end_time": 554616.0,
      "text": "to ask them to be your sponsor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 554640.0,
      "end_time": 558376.0,
      "text": "they will in fact answer in the affirmative."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 558400.0,
      "end_time": 562256.0,
      "text": "Now, if you&#39;re with me and you agree that you have to have a sponsor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 562280.0,
      "end_time": 566199.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s talk about how you identify a sponsor."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 567400.0,
      "end_time": 568976.0,
      "text": "Well, if you&#39;re looking for a sponsor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 569000.0,
      "end_time": 572136.0,
      "text": "they need to have three primary characteristics."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 572160.0,
      "end_time": 577415.0,
      "text": "Number one, they need to have a seat at the decision-making table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 577440.0,
      "end_time": 580496.0,
      "text": "they need to have exposure to your work"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 580520.0,
      "end_time": 584136.0,
      "text": "in order to have credibility behind closed doors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 584160.0,
      "end_time": 585856.0,
      "text": "and they need to have some juice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 585880.0,
      "end_time": 588736.0,
      "text": "or let me say it differently, they&#39;d better have some power."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 588760.0,
      "end_time": 592216.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really important that they have those three things."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 592240.0,
      "end_time": 594976.0,
      "text": "And then once you have identified the person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 595000.0,
      "end_time": 597560.0,
      "text": "how do you ask for one?"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 597800.0,
      "end_time": 598736.0,
      "text": "The script goes like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 598760.0,
      "end_time": 603616.0,
      "text": "\"Jim, I&#39;m really interested in getting promoted this year."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 603640.0,
      "end_time": 606175.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve had an amazing year"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 606200.0,
      "end_time": 611736.0,
      "text": "and I cannot show this organization anything else to prove my worthiness"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 611760.0,
      "end_time": 613976.0,
      "text": "or my readiness for this promotion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 614000.0,
      "end_time": 618216.0,
      "text": "but I am aware that somebody has to be behind closed doors"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 618240.0,
      "end_time": 621256.0,
      "text": "arguing on my behalf and pounding the table."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 621280.0,
      "end_time": 625216.0,
      "text": "You know me, you know my work and you are aware of the client feedback,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 625240.0,
      "end_time": 629336.0,
      "text": "and I hope that you will feel comfortable arguing on my behalf.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 629360.0,
      "end_time": 630976.0,
      "text": "If Jim knows you"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 631000.0,
      "end_time": 633496.0,
      "text": "and you have any kind of a relationship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 633520.0,
      "end_time": 636936.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a very high probability that he will answer yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 636960.0,
      "end_time": 638296.0,
      "text": "and if he says yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 638320.0,
      "end_time": 640696.0,
      "text": "he will endeavor to get it done for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 640720.0,
      "end_time": 643736.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s also a shot that Jim might say no,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 643760.0,
      "end_time": 645656.0,
      "text": "and if he says no, in my opinion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 645680.0,
      "end_time": 648415.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s only three reasons that he would tell you no."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 648440.0,
      "end_time": 653160.0,
      "text": "The first is he doesn&#39;t think that he has enough exposure to your work"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 653400.0,
      "end_time": 656136.0,
      "text": "to have real credibility behind closed doors"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 656160.0,
      "end_time": 659776.0,
      "text": "to be impactful and effective on your behalf."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 659800.0,
      "end_time": 661776.0,
      "text": "The second reason he may tell you no"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 661800.0,
      "end_time": 665175.0,
      "text": "is that you think he has the juice to get it done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 665200.0,
      "end_time": 668416.0,
      "text": "but he knows that he does not have the power to do it"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 668440.0,
      "end_time": 671696.0,
      "text": "and he is not going to admit that in that conversation with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 671720.0,
      "end_time": 672856.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 672880.0,
      "end_time": 675536.0,
      "text": "And the third reason that he would tell you no,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 675560.0,
      "end_time": 676776.0,
      "text": "he doesn&#39;t like you."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 676800.0,
      "end_time": 678160.0,
      "text": "He doesn&#39;t like you."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 678400.0,
      "end_time": 679175.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 679200.0,
      "end_time": 681496.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s something that could happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 681520.0,
      "end_time": 685816.0,
      "text": "But even that will be valuable information for you"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 685840.0,
      "end_time": 689896.0,
      "text": "that will help to inform your next conversation with a sponsor"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 689920.0,
      "end_time": 693360.0,
      "text": "that might make it a little bit more impactful."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 694160.0,
      "end_time": 697656.0,
      "text": "I cannot tell you how important it is to have a sponsor."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 697680.0,
      "end_time": 701976.0,
      "text": "It is the critical relationship in your career."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 702000.0,
      "end_time": 704856.0,
      "text": "A mentor, frankly, is a nice to have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 704880.0,
      "end_time": 708896.0,
      "text": "but you can survive a long time in your career without a mentor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 708920.0,
      "end_time": 714496.0,
      "text": "but you are not going to ascend in any organization without a sponsor."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 714520.0,
      "end_time": 718896.0,
      "text": "It is so critical that you should ask yourself regularly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 718920.0,
      "end_time": 721536.0,
      "text": "\"Who&#39;s carrying my paper into the room?"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 721560.0,
      "end_time": 723935.0,
      "text": "Who is carrying my paper into the room?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 723960.0,
      "end_time": 727696.0,
      "text": "And if you can&#39;t answer who is carrying your paper into the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 727720.0,
      "end_time": 731216.0,
      "text": "then I will tell you to divert some of your hardworking energies"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 731240.0,
      "end_time": 734496.0,
      "text": "into investing in a sponsor relationship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 734520.0,
      "end_time": 737696.0,
      "text": "because it will be critical to your success."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 737720.0,
      "end_time": 740536.0,
      "text": "And as I close, let me give a word"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 740560.0,
      "end_time": 742719.0,
      "text": "to the would-be sponsors that are in the room."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 743680.0,
      "end_time": 746736.0,
      "text": "If you have been invited into the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 746760.0,
      "end_time": 750160.0,
      "text": "know that you have a seat at that table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 750400.0,
      "end_time": 752496.0,
      "text": "and if you have a seat at the table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 752520.0,
      "end_time": 755175.0,
      "text": "you have a responsibility to speak."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 755200.0,
      "end_time": 760176.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t waste your power worrying about what people are going to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 760200.0,
      "end_time": 763296.0,
      "text": "and whether or not they think you might be supporting someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 763320.0,
      "end_time": 765736.0,
      "text": "just because they look like you."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 765760.0,
      "end_time": 768960.0,
      "text": "If somebody is worthy of your currency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 769880.0,
      "end_time": 771616.0,
      "text": "spend it."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 771640.0,
      "end_time": 774696.0,
      "text": "One thing I have learned after several decades on Wall Street"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 774720.0,
      "end_time": 778136.0,
      "text": "is the way to grow your power is to give it away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 778160.0,
      "end_time": 780376.0,
      "text": "and your voice is at the heart."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 780400.0,
      "end_time": 785360.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 786360.0,
      "end_time": 791160.0,
      "text": "And your voice is at the heart of your power."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 791960.0,
      "end_time": 793176.0,
      "text": "Use it."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 793200.0,
      "end_time": 794416.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 794440.0,
      "end_time": 800600.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}